- ğŸ“¦ Admin Dashboard for product management (Add/Edit/Delete)
- ğŸ¤– Content-Based Product Recommendation System
- ğŸ¯ Personalized "Recommended For You" products (using localStorage)
- ğŸ’» Responsive Netflix-style UI with Bootstrap 5 styling
- ğŸ”§ Flask API backend with MongoDB

